										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>夏天是一个炎热的季节，同时在这个季节里有很多好吃的水果上市，除了西瓜、荔枝等，而在华南地区，华南地区还有一种不起眼的水果在夏季“大行其道”，它就是黄皮。黄皮是继荔枝上市之后又一个新的夏季成熟果实，北方很少见甚至很陌生，它是两广、福建等地区特有的水果，它的大小色泽皆与龙眼相似，黄灿灿的，果肉柔滑细腻，酸甜开胃，是很多“老广”的心头好，也因此得与荔枝齐名。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-315" title="d3960c8f7ea84968ba27d0685607a55a" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d3960c8f7ea84968ba27d0685607a55a.jpg" alt="d3960c8f7ea84968ba27d0685607a55a" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d3960c8f7ea84968ba27d0685607a55a.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d3960c8f7ea84968ba27d0685607a55a-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/d3960c8f7ea84968ba27d0685607a55a-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="3">与荔枝、龙眼吃多了会上火不同，这个吃多多也不怕。在广东有句谚语：“饥食荔枝，饱食黄皮”，意思是吃黄皮果可消除腹胀、助消化，除此之外，它还有理气化痰止咳、生津止渴等功效，素有“正气果”的美誉。6月，吃荔枝不如吃它，现在是黄皮果采摘的季节，除了生吃，我们还可制成蜜饯当零食食用，不含添加剂，酸甜可口，连皮也能吃下去，而且保存时间比鲜果更长。话不多说，一起来看看这蜜饯黄皮的详细做法吧。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-316" title="3cab87bf04d04698baed39fefd63caba" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3cab87bf04d04698baed39fefd63caba.jpg" alt="3cab87bf04d04698baed39fefd63caba" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3cab87bf04d04698baed39fefd63caba.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3cab87bf04d04698baed39fefd63caba-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3cab87bf04d04698baed39fefd63caba-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="4">【食材】：黄皮果 适量、冰糖 100克、盐 适量</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317" title="f3965dfed75a4318a9c58298f27fe925" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f3965dfed75a4318a9c58298f27fe925.jpg" alt="f3965dfed75a4318a9c58298f27fe925" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f3965dfed75a4318a9c58298f27fe925.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f3965dfed75a4318a9c58298f27fe925-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/f3965dfed75a4318a9c58298f27fe925-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="5">1、黄皮去梗，最好不用拔，容易弄破果肉，抓一把盐撒上，倒入清水浸泡半小时再搓洗干净，由于果皮是要吃的，所以一定要清洗干净。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-319" title="7737eae6c8c24e619d796060de76f809" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7737eae6c8c24e619d796060de76f809.jpg" alt="7737eae6c8c24e619d796060de76f809" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7737eae6c8c24e619d796060de76f809.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7737eae6c8c24e619d796060de76f809-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7737eae6c8c24e619d796060de76f809-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">2、把黄皮放入锅里，大火蒸20~30分钟左右，具体时间视不同的火候，一般蒸到大部分黄皮已经开裂就算好了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318" title="7ad99436a1a84bc3848c45a99a83a2c8" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7ad99436a1a84bc3848c45a99a83a2c8.jpg" alt="7ad99436a1a84bc3848c45a99a83a2c8" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7ad99436a1a84bc3848c45a99a83a2c8.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7ad99436a1a84bc3848c45a99a83a2c8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7ad99436a1a84bc3848c45a99a83a2c8-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="7">3、放冷后，把黄皮果里面果核全部挤出来，保留皮肉。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-320" title="a4077e3767ad4a69b6a9a62aebb89b33" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a4077e3767ad4a69b6a9a62aebb89b33.jpg" alt="a4077e3767ad4a69b6a9a62aebb89b33" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a4077e3767ad4a69b6a9a62aebb89b33.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a4077e3767ad4a69b6a9a62aebb89b33-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/a4077e3767ad4a69b6a9a62aebb89b33-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="8">4、处理好的黄皮放入干净的平底锅里面，倒入冰糖（白糖也可以），不用放水，大火煮开后改中小火翻炒出汁；</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-321" title="2fa71e234e474f53a49b8c45f4c2662f" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2fa71e234e474f53a49b8c45f4c2662f.jpg" alt="2fa71e234e474f53a49b8c45f4c2662f" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2fa71e234e474f53a49b8c45f4c2662f.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2fa71e234e474f53a49b8c45f4c2662f-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2fa71e234e474f53a49b8c45f4c2662f-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9">5、冰糖融化后小火慢慢熬，一定要经常搅拌避免粘锅，这一步是非常费体力和时间的，需要有耐心，直至糖汁变少收干，变得粘稠就完成咯。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-323" title="ad814d003bdd4af096d4c8f627cd02fb" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ad814d003bdd4af096d4c8f627cd02fb.jpg" alt="ad814d003bdd4af096d4c8f627cd02fb" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ad814d003bdd4af096d4c8f627cd02fb.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ad814d003bdd4af096d4c8f627cd02fb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ad814d003bdd4af096d4c8f627cd02fb-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="10">放凉后再装到无水无油的瓶子中，放入冰箱内冷藏保存，平时也可以拿来吃或冲水喝，健脾开胃、清热消暑、还有止咳化痰的功效。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-322" title="7b7adb36cd44492a9761fa6ef1c93565" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7b7adb36cd44492a9761fa6ef1c93565.jpg" alt="7b7adb36cd44492a9761fa6ef1c93565" width="936" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7b7adb36cd44492a9761fa6ef1c93565.jpg 936w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7b7adb36cd44492a9761fa6ef1c93565-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7b7adb36cd44492a9761fa6ef1c93565-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 936px) 100vw, 936px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="11">【小提示】：买回来的黄皮品种不同，每个人对酸甜的接受度也不同，所以加冰糖的量要根据自己的口味和实际情况做调整。</p>
